00:42:08.319 --> 00:42:11.190
your soil.

00:42:11.200 --> 00:42:14.470
Where are you

00:42:14.470 --> 00:42:14.480
sowing?

00:42:14.480 --> 00:42:16.470
Whatsoever a man sows, that will he also

00:42:16.480 --> 00:42:19.109
