00:42:20.720 --> 00:42:22.150
the rocks. Sowing into the rocks and

00:42:22.160 --> 00:42:23.510
they go, "Well, is it going to produce

00:42:23.520 --> 00:42:25.910
this time?"I'm like, "Well, no. If it

00:42:25.920 --> 00:42:28.069
