00:42:28.079 --> 00:42:33.430
it isn't going to produce

00:42:33.430 --> 00:42:33.440
now."Check

00:42:33.440 --> 00:42:35.829
where you're giving

00:42:35.839 --> 00:42:37.990
and be smart and strategic with your

00:42:38.000 --> 00:42:41.109
