00:42:56.390 --> 00:42:56.400
giving.

00:42:56.400 --> 00:43:00.390
Show me, Lord,

00:43:00.400 --> 00:43:02.790
where I'm getting fed. But if you're

00:43:02.800 --> 00:43:04.309
not getting fed there, and then when you

00:43:04.309 --> 00:43:04.319
sow

00:43:04.319 --> 00:43:06.150
there and the cankerworm is eating it

00:43:06.160 --> 00:43:09.430
