00:43:14.400 --> 00:43:17.589
"Well, there's fruit

00:43:17.589 --> 00:43:17.599
there."So

00:43:17.599 --> 00:43:19.750
then you have to check your love walk,

00:43:19.760 --> 00:43:21.349
and people don't want to do that. Well,

00:43:21.359 --> 00:43:22.790
how are you talking to your wife? How

00:43:22.800 --> 00:43:24.630
