00:43:34.240 --> 00:43:36.069
Because faith works by love, and people

00:43:36.079 --> 00:43:38.870
don't want to hear that either. Well, you've got strife in the house all the time, so you can't always blame it on the

00:43:38.870 --> 00:43:38.880
ground. How are you treating one another? Because faith works by love, and people don't want to hear that.

00:43:38.880 --> 00:43:40.550
Do you know the Bible says that

00:43:40.560 --> 00:43:42.790
if you treat your wife like trash and

00:43:42.800 --> 00:43:45.109
you don't respect her, husbands, your prayers

00:43:45.119 --> 00:43:48.390
will be hindered?

00:43:48.400 --> 00:43:50.710
