00:56:36.079 --> 00:56:38.470
water is gone. No bag limits on any

00:56:38.480 --> 00:56:40.549
species through May 13th.

00:56:40.559 --> 00:56:41.910
All of these fish are going to die.

00:56:41.910 --> 00:56:41.920
Everything—I

00:56:41.920 --> 00:56:43.670
mean, even the fish

00:56:43.680 --> 00:56:45.510
that everybody keeps, they're

00:56:45.520 --> 00:56:47.670
going to die. Whatever people don't

00:56:47.680 --> 00:56:49.589
come and take, the fish are going to be

00:56:49.599 --> 00:56:50.789
in the bottom of the lake. They're going

00:56:50.799 --> 00:56:53.510
to be bone-dry skeletons by next year.

00:56:53.520 --> 00:56:55.190
Travis Sawyer is a fishing guide here.

00:56:55.200 --> 00:56:56.950
He says he's running free trips for

00:56:56.960 --> 00:56:58.470
people so that they can enjoy the water

00:56:58.480 --> 00:57:00.150
while it's still here. This is one of

00:57:00.160 --> 00:57:01.750
his favorite places to fish, and he says

00:57:01.760 --> 00:57:04.309
that people from all over the world fly

00:57:04.319 --> 00:57:06.390
here for the fish. He said,

00:57:06.400 --> 00:57:08.710
'We're draining this lake bone

00:57:08.710 --> 00:57:08.720
dry.'So

00:57:08.720 --> 00:57:11.190
anything that people don't

00:57:11.200 --> 00:57:14.309
take is going to be killed.

00:57:14.319 --> 00:57:16.069
The last time that Antero was drained was

00:57:16.079 --> 00:57:18.630
2015 for a dam rehabilitation project.

00:57:18.640 --> 00:57:21.349
Before that, it was 2002, also a drought

00:57:21.359 --> 00:57:23.190
year. It took several years for the fish

00:57:23.200 --> 00:57:25.349
to become healthy again here after that.

00:57:25.359 --> 00:57:27.109
We've had bad droughts before, but

00:57:27.119 --> 00:57:29.510
nothing like this one. I'm Mark. I cover

00:57:29.520 --> 00:57:31.190
Colorado. Follow for more stories like

00:57:31.200 --> 00:57:33.189
this one.

00:57:33.440 --> 00:57:36.230
So, all those fish—if you like fish and

00:57:36.240 --> 00:57:37.990
you live in Colorado, that might be a

00:57:38.000 --> 00:57:41.589
fun day. I love fishing. And I tell you

00:57:41.599 --> 00:57:43.349
what, that would be a fun day for

00:57:43.359 --> 00:57:45.990
me. I'd put all those things in an ice chest

00:57:46.000 --> 00:57:47.910
and freeze them.

00:57:47.920 --> 00:57:50.470
There's nothing better

00:57:50.470 --> 00:57:50.480
than

00:57:50.480 --> 00:57:54.069
trout to me. In fact,

00:57:59.200 --> 00:58:02.870
my slobber comes just thinking

00:58:02.870 --> 00:58:02.880
about it.

00:58:02.880 --> 00:58:04.630
I've been eating protein shakes and

00:58:04.640 --> 00:58:06.470
little bits of chicken.

00:58:06.480 --> 00:58:09.349
Oh, good Lord,

00:58:09.359 --> 00:58:10.950
I'm trying to get this weight down as

00:58:10.960 --> 00:58:14.069
fast as I can. But I walked five miles

00:58:14.079 --> 00:58:15.589
yesterday.

00:58:15.599 --> 00:58:17.990
I was really excited about it. I

00:58:18.000 --> 00:58:21.270
told

00:58:21.280 --> 00:58:23.990
Diana my face felt like

00:58:24.000 --> 00:58:26.069
charcoal.

00:58:26.079 --> 00:58:27.589
But five miles in a day is pretty good

00:58:27.599 --> 00:58:30.230
for Brandon Biggs.

00:58:32.000 --> 00:58:39.345
All right.

00:58:45.359 --> 00:58:48.549
Look what Jesus is

00:58:48.559 --> 00:58:51.510
doing.

00:58:51.520 --> 00:58:53.670
In Russia,

00:58:58.960 --> 00:59:03.910
Putin is scheming.

00:59:07.359 --> 00:59:10.230
Father, we just thank you for the body

00:59:10.240 --> 00:59:13.510
as we come before you boldly

00:59:13.520 --> 00:59:15.030
into your throne. Father, if you

00:59:15.040 --> 00:59:17.430
want to show us things about that which

00:59:17.440 --> 00:59:19.510
is to come, we're here.

00:59:19.520 --> 00:59:22.390
We're always here

00:59:22.400 --> 00:59:25.109
just to stay by

00:59:25.119 --> 00:59:26.789
your feet and say, 'God, we love

00:59:26.789 --> 00:59:26.799
you.'We

00:59:26.799 --> 00:59:28.710
want to hear everything.

00:59:28.720 --> 00:59:30.950
I'll sit in your lap and just listen to

00:59:30.960 --> 00:59:34.870
your heartbeat

00:59:34.870 --> 00:59:34.880
and

00:59:34.880 --> 00:59:37.910
your breath.

00:59:37.920 --> 00:59:39.990
Every breath that proceeds out of you,

00:59:40.000 --> 00:59:43.030
Father, I want to be close to you.

00:59:43.040 --> 00:59:44.789
Father, I thank you that we hear

00:59:44.799 --> 00:59:47.510
you and a stranger's voice we will not

00:59:47.520 --> 00:59:50.710
follow. We lift up this body, God, and

00:59:50.720 --> 00:59:52.630
we're so thankful for your son,

00:59:52.640 --> 00:59:55.589
Jesus.

00:59:55.599 --> 00:59:58.150
Thank you, Father, that he suffered and

00:59:58.160 --> 01:00:00.069
died for every single one of us, that we

01:00:00.079 --> 01:00:02.309
walk in victory.

01:00:02.319 --> 01:00:04.150
Thank you, Lord, that we go from glory

01:00:04.160 --> 01:00:07.030
to glory. I thank you, Lord, that we are

01:00:07.040 --> 01:00:09.829
healed and whole and well. We don't

01:00:09.839 --> 01:00:11.829
have to have sickness and disease in our

01:00:11.839 --> 01:00:14.390
bodies anymore because by your stripes,

01:00:14.400 --> 01:00:17.270
we're healed. We take this body in

01:00:17.280 --> 01:00:19.589
the name of Jesus and we give you all

01:00:19.599 --> 01:00:21.430
the glory, honor, and praise for what you did

01:00:21.440 --> 01:00:25.430
for us. Amen.

01:00:25.440 --> 01:00:29.829
We apply

01:00:33.440 --> 01:00:36.549
the blood of Jesus

01:00:36.559 --> 01:00:39.349
over us and we thank you, Father, that

01:00:39.359 --> 01:00:42.710
it never loses its power.

01:00:47.760 --> 01:00:50.549
It covers us from the top of

01:00:50.559 --> 01:00:52.630
our head to the soles of our feet,

01:00:52.640 --> 01:00:54.710
uninterrupted and unhindered by any

01:00:54.720 --> 01:00:57.829
satanic or demonic force. We rebuke the devil

01:00:57.829 --> 01:00:57.839
in the name

01:00:57.839 --> 01:00:59.910
of Jesus.

01:01:18.720 --> 01:01:20.630
Amen.

01:01:23.280 --> 01:01:25.510
Over our children, our wives, and our

01:01:25.520 --> 01:01:27.670
finances.

01:01:37.520 --> 01:01:40.710
Father,

01:01:46.000 --> 01:01:50.390
open the eyes of our heart.

01:01:54.000 --> 01:01:58.549
I want

01:02:46.480 --> 01:02:52.390
to see you high and lifted up,

01:02:52.400 --> 01:02:58.230
shining in the light of your glory.

01:02:58.240 --> 01:03:03.270
Pour out your power and love as we sing

01:03:03.280 --> 01:03:08.549
holy, holy, holy.

01:03:22.160 --> 01:03:32.710
I want to see you.

01:03:32.720 --> 01:03:34.230
Lord,

01:03:34.240 --> 01:03:37.829
there

01:03:37.839 --> 01:03:44.950
are

01:04:21.520 --> 01:04:23.109
so many people here

01:04:23.119 --> 01:04:24.789
tonight that are thirsty.

01:04:27.039 --> 01:04:29.029
We lift up our cup before you

01:04:29.029 --> 01:04:29.039
and

01:04:29.039 --> 01:04:32.870
say, 'Fill

01:04:37.910 --> 01:04:37.920
it.'Come

01:04:42.079 --> 01:04:45.109
and quench

01:04:45.119 --> 01:04:49.589
this thirsting of our soul.

01:04:49.599 --> 01:04:52.470
Bread of heaven,

01:04:52.480 --> 01:04:58.549
feed us till we want no more.

01:04:58.559 --> 01:05:01.190
Fill our cup,

01:05:01.200 --> 01:05:09.109
fill it up, and make

01:05:43.839 --> 01:05:51.190
us whole.

01:06:35.839 --> 01:06:43.270
If I could just sit with you a while.

01:06:43.280 --> 01:06:50.470
I need you to hold me

01:06:50.480 --> 01:06:55.109
moment by moment

01:06:55.119 --> 01:06:57.990
till forever

01:06:58.000 --> 01:07:04.630
passes by.

01:08:53.440 --> 01:08:56.070
Fill the cups of

01:08:56.070 --> 01:08:56.080
those

01:08:56.080 --> 01:08:57.829
here tonight. They're so

01:08:57.839 --> 01:09:00.390
thirsty,

01:09:00.400 --> 01:09:02.390
Holy Spirit.

01:09:02.400 --> 01:09:08.070
Do what you do best.

01:09:08.080 --> 01:09:11.430
We're wall-to-wall, Holy Ghost, and we

01:09:11.440 --> 01:09:14.070
yield to that tonight.

01:09:14.080 --> 01:09:17.510
We yield to you.

01:09:17.520 --> 01:09:22.309
Become so real.

01:09:26.159 --> 01:09:28.870
The tangible, weighty presence of the

01:09:28.880 --> 01:09:31.430
Lord

01:09:31.440 --> 01:09:38.937
that changes you from the inside out.

01:09:41.520 --> 01:09:46.950
Do what you do best, oh God.

01:09:46.960 --> 01:09:50.630
Fill the cup.

01:09:50.640 --> 01:09:56.070
Life pulls it, making us dry.

01:09:56.080 --> 01:09:58.950
Life's hardships and circumstances make

01:09:58.960 --> 01:10:05.189
us dry. We leak out.

01:10:05.199 --> 01:10:08.550
But don't just fill it; make it overflow

01:10:08.560 --> 01:10:11.189
so everybody else can taste and see that

01:10:11.199 --> 01:10:14.070
the Lord is so good.

01:10:14.080 --> 01:10:16.070
It's the goodness of God that

01:10:16.080 --> 01:10:21.270
brings men to repentance.

01:10:21.280 --> 01:10:26.870
When they see us, they see Jesus in us.

01:10:26.880 --> 01:10:29.430
Christ in me,

01:10:29.440 --> 01:10:31.993
the hope of glory.

01:10:36.560 --> 01:10:38.470
We love

01:10:38.480 --> 01:10:41.590
you.

01:10:41.600 --> 01:10:45.590
Oh, how we love

01:10:45.600 --> 01:10:47.510
you.

01:11:02.159 --> 01:11:06.950
I'll have no other,

01:11:06.960 --> 01:11:11.830
for I love you only.

01:11:11.840 --> 01:11:17.030
I'll never forsake you

01:11:17.040 --> 01:11:23.990
or leave you alone.

01:11:24.000 --> 01:11:27.830
I love

01:11:27.840 --> 01:11:31.270
you.

01:11:31.280 --> 01:11:35.830
Oh, how I love

01:11:35.840 --> 01:11:37.510
you.

01:11:50.480 --> 01:11:55.189
Here in your arms,

01:11:55.199 --> 01:11:59.110
I'll always be

01:11:59.120 --> 01:12:03.430
at rest in your precious love

01:12:03.440 --> 01:12:18.229
you have for me.

01:12:18.239 --> 01:12:22.870
We worship you.

01:12:22.880 --> 01:12:26.950
We're so grateful.

01:12:26.960 --> 01:12:30.550
We take the care out of our prayers.

01:12:30.560 --> 01:12:33.110
The cares of this life try to choke

01:12:33.120 --> 01:12:36.709
out everything:

01:12:36.719 --> 01:12:40.149
cares for finances, health,

01:12:40.159 --> 01:12:43.030
marriages, our kids,

01:12:43.040 --> 01:12:45.910
work, where we live,

01:12:45.910 --> 01:12:45.920
and

01:12:45.920 --> 01:12:48.149
where we go to church. There

01:12:48.149 --> 01:12:48.159
are

01:12:48.159 --> 01:12:50.390
so many cares. The cares

01:12:50.400 --> 01:12:53.830
try to choke out everything,

01:12:53.840 --> 01:12:59.830
but we cast our cares upon you tonight.

01:12:59.840 --> 01:13:02.645
We give it to you.

01:13:02.655 --> 01:13:04.310
We don't need to carry it

01:13:04.320 --> 01:13:07.590
anyway.

01:13:07.600 --> 01:13:11.350
We cast our cares on you, for you care

01:13:11.360 --> 01:13:14.435
for us.

01:13:16.159 --> 01:13:18.149
We're so grateful for all that you've

01:13:18.159 --> 01:13:20.070
done, all you've provided, all you've

01:13:20.080 --> 01:13:23.430
done for our health, for our bodies, for

01:13:23.440 --> 01:13:25.430
everything.

01:13:25.440 --> 01:13:27.189
Even when we don't see the full

01:13:27.199 --> 01:13:29.270
manifestation of what we've been

01:13:29.280 --> 01:13:33.110
believing for yet, God, you are still so

01:13:33.120 --> 01:13:36.870
faithful to us.

01:13:36.880 --> 01:13:39.430
We're not moved by what we see. We're

01:13:39.440 --> 01:13:41.830
not moved by what we feel. We're moved

01:13:41.840 --> 01:13:44.229
by what the word of God says. And we're

01:13:44.239 --> 01:13:46.870
fully persuaded

01:13:46.880 --> 01:13:49.510
that what God, you have promised, you

01:13:49.520 --> 01:13:55.046
are able also to perform.

01:13:55.679 --> 01:14:05.910
And we take the care out of our prayer.

01:14:05.920 --> 01:14:10.070
But with thanksgiving,

01:14:10.080 --> 01:14:11.830
we let our requests be made

01:14:11.840 --> 01:14:14.709
known unto you.

01:14:14.719 --> 01:14:17.590
Thank you, Father.

01:14:22.239 --> 01:14:24.550
There were stipulations before

01:14:24.560 --> 01:14:30.390
it: with thanksgiving.

01:14:30.400 --> 01:14:35.830
We thank him first. We praise him first,

01:14:35.840 --> 01:14:38.070
for he knows what we have need of before

01:14:38.080 --> 01:14:40.790
we even ask.

01:14:40.800 --> 01:14:43.750
We thank him first with thanksgiving. We

01:14:43.760 --> 01:14:46.870
take the care out of our prayer,

01:14:46.880 --> 01:14:50.229
but with thanksgiving.

01:14:50.239 --> 01:14:52.950
Thank you, Lord.

01:15:14.320 --> 01:15:17.350
A thankful heart moves the Father.

01:15:17.350 --> 01:15:17.360
It

01:15:17.360 --> 01:15:18.870
is

01:15:18.880 --> 01:15:21.189
giving

01:15:21.199 --> 01:15:23.990
a grateful attitude.

01:15:24.000 --> 01:15:28.310
Thank you

01:15:28.320 --> 01:15:30.310
for even the things we don't see

01:15:30.320 --> 01:15:33.030
manifested yet in our lives. We're so

01:15:33.040 --> 01:15:36.550
grateful for what we do have. We're so

01:15:36.560 --> 01:15:39.110
thankful for where we are. And we're so

01:15:39.120 --> 01:15:42.709
grateful that we're not where we

01:15:42.709 --> 01:15:42.719
were.

01:15:42.719 --> 01:15:46.310
For we're going from

01:15:46.320 --> 01:15:57.030
glory to glory.

01:15:57.040 --> 01:15:59.030
Lord, we're so grateful, Father, that

01:15:59.040 --> 01:16:01.990
you would visit us,

01:16:02.000 --> 01:16:09.350
that you call us your own.

01:16:09.360 --> 01:16:12.550
You adopted us and you accepted us into

01:16:12.560 --> 01:16:14.310
your

01:16:14.310 --> 01:16:14.320
house.

01:16:14.320 --> 01:16:20.390
And you said, "I make you my own

01:16:20.400 --> 01:16:27.430
joint heirs with Jesus

01:16:27.430 --> 01:16:27.440
Christ."Thank

01:16:27.440 --> 01:16:32.470
you, Father.

01:16:32.480 --> 01:16:38.229
As he is, so are we in this world.

01:16:38.239 --> 01:16:40.950
Greater works will we do

01:16:40.960 --> 01:16:43.430
because he goes unto the

01:16:43.440 --> 01:16:45.830
Father. He sent us a Comforter, the Holy

01:16:45.840 --> 01:16:53.510
Spirit. He dwells on the inside of us.

01:16:53.520 --> 01:16:55.910
When Christ sat down, we sat down with

01:16:55.920 --> 01:17:03.110
him.

01:17:10.960 --> 01:17:13.990
Thank you, Father.

01:17:14.000 --> 01:17:16.630
The same Holy Spirit that raised Jesus

01:17:16.640 --> 01:17:18.870
Christ from the dead dwells on the

01:17:18.880 --> 01:17:22.229
inside of me.

01:17:22.239 --> 01:17:25.669
He dwells on the inside of me richly by

01:17:25.679 --> 01:17:27.510
faith.

01:17:27.520 --> 01:17:31.350
I'm wall-to-wall Holy Ghost.

01:17:31.360 --> 01:17:35.590
Can these bones

01:17:35.590 --> 01:17:35.600
live—the

01:17:35.600 --> 01:17:39.669
dry bones upon this earth? Can

01:17:39.679 --> 01:17:45.590
these bones live?

01:17:45.600 --> 01:17:49.910
They can, and they will,

01:17:49.920 --> 01:17:55.430
and they do.

01:17:55.440 --> 01:17:59.270
We speak to the dry bones in the church.

01:18:02.159 --> 01:18:04.709
We speak to the dry bones behind the

01:18:04.719 --> 01:18:06.470
pulpit.

01:18:06.480 --> 01:18:11.110
All these dry bones behind the pulpit,

01:18:11.120 --> 01:18:16.950
we say you will live.

01:18:16.960 --> 01:18:21.669
Be refreshed with the living water

01:18:21.679 --> 01:18:23.910
stirred from the top of your head to the

01:18:23.920 --> 01:18:30.149
soles of your feet.

01:18:54.560 --> 01:18:59.750
Oh Father,

01:18:59.760 --> 01:19:03.430
we glorify your name

01:19:03.440 --> 01:19:07.189
in all the earth.

01:19:07.199 --> 01:19:11.110
We

01:20:07.280 --> 01:20:11.189
magnify

01:20:11.199 --> 01:20:15.990
your name

01:20:31.199 --> 01:20:58.070
in all the earth.

01:24:18.159 --> 01:24:22.149
I see the glory. I see it on the people.

01:24:22.159 --> 01:24:23.750
And many of you are walking in

01:24:23.760 --> 01:24:26.149
the greatest fountain

01:24:26.149 --> 01:24:26.159
of

01:24:26.159 --> 01:24:29.990
glory on you. The

01:24:29.990 --> 01:24:30.000
glow

01:24:30.000 --> 01:24:31.910
as you come up higher with him every

01:24:31.920 --> 01:24:34.629
day. As you come up higher with him

01:24:34.639 --> 01:24:37.910
every day, a greater manifestation of

01:24:37.920 --> 01:24:49.350
the glory will come on you each day.

01:24:49.360 --> 01:24:50.950
There's so many distractions

01:24:50.960 --> 01:24:53.189
he's talking

01:24:53.189 --> 01:24:53.199
about—distractions

01:24:53.199 --> 01:24:55.750
pulling you out

01:24:55.760 --> 01:25:00.390
of that river.

01:25:00.400 --> 01:25:03.270
You'll

01:25:03.280 --> 01:25:06.709
have to draw a line concerning the

01:25:06.719 --> 01:25:11.510
things that are important to you:

01:25:11.520 --> 01:25:14.629
coming up higher with him each day.

01:25:14.639 --> 01:25:17.990
For what's coming,

01:25:18.000 --> 01:25:19.669
do you understand? He said, "For what's

01:25:19.679 --> 01:25:23.750
coming."You

01:25:23.760 --> 01:25:27.350
have a short little time right here

01:25:27.360 --> 01:25:30.310
to get your heart ready.

01:25:30.320 --> 01:25:34.310
It's all hands on deck.

01:25:34.320 --> 01:25:36.470
For the harvest is plentiful and the

01:25:36.470 --> 01:25:36.480
laborers

01:25:36.480 --> 01:25:39.430
are few.

01:25:39.440 --> 01:25:42.950
And I have great things for you to do,

01:25:42.960 --> 01:25:45.030
and the greatest manifestations will

01:25:45.040 --> 01:25:48.149
flow through you, for the harvest

01:25:48.159 --> 01:26:00.470
is plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:26:00.480 --> 01:26:04.070
And there will be nothing

01:26:04.080 --> 01:26:05.910
holding you back

01:26:05.910 --> 01:26:05.920
from

01:26:05.920 --> 01:26:09.110
what you've tried to achieve.

01:26:09.120 --> 01:26:11.110
The greater works will flow

01:26:11.120 --> 01:26:13.270
through your hands and the

01:26:13.280 --> 01:26:15.189
demonstrations and the manifestations.

01:26:15.199 --> 01:26:17.590
I've seen it.

